{"tid":1347360,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"<逆向思維> 發展香港式共產主義","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:26:23.000Z","uid":182207,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f21551384ed13d6e2364fc21e68da3e25199918a","tid":1347360,"uid":182207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:56:14.000Z","msg":"可以試下反其道而行<br />\n依家啲藍絲話中國幾好幾好<br />\n我地就比佢地體驗下以前佢地要走難落嚟嘅中國有幾好<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqmUnsc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiqmUnsc.gif&h=9ef590f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNwQFdS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNwQFdS.gif&h=2bdb3b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日日上街去中環老銅屌尻班西裝佬，啲死中產。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRSXked.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRSXked.gif&h=6d39adc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再去啲圍村入面批鬥丁權<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2SxMdzp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SxMdzp.gif&h=ecdf3105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地連登愛國青年理應跟隨毛主席嘅步伐<br />\n一齊加入香港式共產主義行列<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DEdGMU1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDEdGMU1.gif&h=0a1aef13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"830c2cad5506aec272bffdf216d5bf480ed734a5","tid":1347360,"uid":182207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7caa44451fee96929822a1b849c7d557930b1617","tid":1347360,"uid":182207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b2c1a2ce4f2fd97d0dfc6541d21e3dcfd341346b","tid":1347360,"uid":182207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d09fc6e84fee394bc245e4219ceefaa9a9c90ded","tid":1347360,"uid":182207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:57:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"74a41